{"tid":1941374,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"六大博企拒提供大型酒店作隔離 賀一誠：澳門人記喺心入面","createTime":"2020-03-24T11:27:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-25T16:25:35.000Z","uid":130626,"like":284,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":51,"replies":[{"pid":"ee15af3e0bc5a44b2554ac48559bb4de57e0a3dd","tid":1941374,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T11:27:25.000Z","msg":"澳門行政長官賀一誠今早會面傳媒時批評，至今仍無博企願意提供綜合體內的大型酒店作為指定隔離酒店，對此感到失望。他呼籲六間博企(新濠國際(200)、永利澳門(1128)、澳博(880)、銀娛(027)、美高梅中國(2282)及金沙中國(1928))要承擔社會責任，「今次都係你哋大考，澳門人睇喺眼入面、記喺心入面」<br />\n<br />\n賀一誠被問到今次武漢肺炎，六間博企的表現會否在未來賭牌申請中加分？他指，感謝博彩業在這次疫情中捐獻口罩，但「唔係話做幾張報紙宣傳下就係社會責任，唔係話送少少嘢出來就係社會責任」。今次疫情是對新一屆特區政府的大考，但也是對六間博企一個大考，認為博企要承擔社會責任。<br />\n<br />\n他指，當地現時沒有確診個案，現階段不需要啟動民防機制，亦不會要求餐廳及賭場停業。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/20200324/I6KNQNAORX2JDRTO23GEEC2O4I/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200324%2FI6KNQNAORX2JDRTO23GEEC2O4I%2F&d=Afoh3Yf6cz19ESyehd0SJxR1GjkmqS0yYYF7Sw2QOJY%3D&h=4caec367\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200324%2FI6KNQNAORX2JDRTO23GEEC2O4I%2F&h=81010162\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/20200324/I6KNQNAORX2JDRTO23GEEC2O4I/</a><br />\n<br />\n好坦白<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed0e5664ad652b8acd3997bd3ba1e1902910cd0c","tid":1941374,"uid":177578,"like":111,"dislike":2,"score":109,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T11:28:30.000Z","msg":"鬥地主<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji